    {
      "id": "fqQhqZJSYG4Cl2FTEode7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -10291.891217803499,
      "y": -313.6169275600091,
      "width": 833.9364208984372,
      "height": 474.00000000000006,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#6741d9",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bHt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1456799270,
      "version": 345,
      "versionNonce": 1003707494,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772355022080,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Lists are like vector and has similar methods\nand function but gives more accessibility to\ninsertion and deletion.\n\nIt uses doubly linked list and stores in\nsequence but non-contiguous manner so\nslower traversal.\n\n**Note** : You cannot access list value using\n`[]` or `at.lst()`",
      "fontSize": 37.92,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Lists are like vector and has similar methods and function but gives more accessibility to insertion and deletion.\n\nIt uses doubly linked list and stores in sequence but non-contiguous manner so slower traversal.\n\n**Note** : You cannot access list value using `[]` or `at.lst()`",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qHDhrfvwUGk7KlTpuq3ec",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4060.2357952544207,
      "y": -3986.9103104512833,
